Needed packages
===============

postgresql-9.0
postgresql-9.0-debversion
python-argparse
python-debian
python-debianbts
python-mako
python-psycopg2
python-pyramid
python-sqlalchemy
python-subversion


Install
=======

as root (more precise: as a postgres superuser):

# su postgres
$ createuser gregoa
Shall the new role be a superuser? (y/n) n
Shall the new role be allowed to create databases? (y/n) y
Shall the new role be allowed to create more new roles? (y/n) n
$ createdb -O gregoa pet
$ psql pet < /usr/share/postgresql/9.0/contrib/debversion.sql

as the created user:

$ ./pet-update -c
$ psql pet
pet=> INSERT INTO repository (name, type, root, webroot) VALUES ('svn','svn','svn://svn.debian.org/pkg-perl','');
pet=> INSERT INTO package (name, repository_id) VALUES ('libboolean-perl', 1);
pet=> \q
$ ./update-package libboolean-perl
